ktuelle Entwicklungen der Energiewirtschaft nachzuvollziehen und kritisch zu bewerten.Die aktuelle Auflage wurde im Vergleich zur 3. Auflage systematisch in der Grundstruktur überarbeitet und dabei Neuentwicklungen in der Energiewirtschaft seit 2012 berücksichtigt.  aThis textbook offers a step-by-step presentation of basic energy economics in general as well as the subsectors of fossil fuels and renewable energy. It illustrates the fundamental economic interconnections of the energy industry and applies these insights to various areas and issues. The 4th edition includes consideration of all new developments in the energy industry.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 4aEnergiebilanzen. 4aErneuerbare Energien. 4aFossile Brennstoffe. 4aKlimaschutzpolitik. 4aRegulierung. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / Microeconomics.2bisacsh  aEnergy trading.  aclimate policy.  aenergy sources.  arenewable energy.1 aHeuterkes, Michael, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aPfaffenberger, Wolfgang, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aRübbelke, Dirk, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aStröbele, Wolfgang, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG OWV ebook Paket Lehrbücher Wirtschaftswiss. 2020z9783110704709oZDB-23-OLW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2020z9783110704624oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831105564760 cprintz978311055632240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311055633940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/97831105